genresAdvancedInfo.name: brazilian stoner rock
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Brazilian stoner rock is a heavy and psychedelic genre that draws inspiration from classic rock and metal, as well as Brazilian folk music. It often features distorted guitars, intricate rhythms, and introspective lyrics that explore themes of spirituality and introspection.
